12.short_description: Founded in 2011, TalentProcess is bringing the best practices and state of the art technology.

18.description:
Founded in 2011, TalentProcess is bringing the best practices and state of the art technology to help recruiters change old practices in to the easiest and must effective way to recruit using the right tools.

TalentProcess is a candidate relationship management system designed by recruiters for recruiters. William Gaber and Monica Graue, veterans in the Executive Search profession designed a Software as a Service (SaaS) platform that pools candidate information from multiple job boards, LinkedIn, social networks, university career centers, and many other networks into one easy to track recruitment process.

TalentProcess allows companies to generate an ongoing talent database and build a recruiter brand through their career site (powered by TalentProcess). This process provides immense value for companies who want to empower their talent attraction strategy and capabilities.

18.description:
Ofelia Feliz is the leading latin american marketplace focused in handmade and creative goods, encouraging and supporting local designers, artists and entrepreneurs.

Based in Buenos Aires, and accelerated in Startup Farm (Brazil), it currently covers Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, Spain, Mexico, Peru, Uruguay and Venezuela.

Felicitas Rossi (former editor-in-chief of OHLALÁ! Magazine) and Juan Agustín Rossi (entrepreneur and developer) started Ofelia Feliz in 2011, to provide the perfect environment to artisans and independent designers to encourage, support and sell their unique products to people that are looking for alternatives to factory-made goods.
